  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p><img src="/media/13067870/inghams-lakes-and-mountains-rail-holidays.jpg" alt="Rail Holidays in the Lakes and Mountains" data-udi="umb://media/2647f2933fd74c4e994b3e3f112e7ccc" /></p>
<h2>Rail Tours in Europe</h2>
<p style="color: #00533a;"><strong>Are you looking for a rail holiday this summer? The <a data-udi="umb://document/96a3e4d143704d3e93793368e4fc0416" href="/{localLink:umb://document/96a3e4d143704d3e93793368e4fc0416}" title="Lakes &amp; Mountains Holidays">Lakes &amp; Mountains</a> are ideal for train travel enthusiasts. Inghams provides you with great railway journeys. Travel from London St Pancras to destinations in <a data-udi="umb://document/01d32bd33c41493f87a033783519ee72" href="/{localLink:umb://document/01d32bd33c41493f87a033783519ee72}#switzerland" title="Rail Holidays" data-anchor="#switzerland">Switzerland</a>, and selected resorts in <a data-udi="umb://document/20c1ee89e76c4eab9b98c48479361bdf" href="/{localLink:umb://document/20c1ee89e76c4eab9b98c48479361bdf}" title="France">France</a> and <a data-udi="umb://document/01d32bd33c41493f87a033783519ee72" href="/{localLink:umb://document/01d32bd33c41493f87a033783519ee72}#Italy" title="Rail Holidays" data-anchor="#Italy">Italy</a>.</strong></p>
<p> </p>
<h2 style="color: #00533a; text-align: center;"><a name="backtotop"></a>Rail Holidays and Rail Tours</h2>
<p> </p>
<div class="g6">
<h3 style="color: #00533a;"><a name="Swiss Tour"></a>Swiss Classic Tour</h3>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/58868750b42d43d78a89df92df2b164f" href="/{localLink:umb://document/58868750b42d43d78a89df92df2b164f}" title="Swiss Classic Escorted Tour"><strong><img src="/media/13067833/inghams-lakes-and-mountains-rail-holidays-bernina-express-swiss-classic-tour.jpg" alt="Swiss Classic Tour" data-udi="umb://media/30d310aca4754eacb3ab9e6edeea5def" /></strong></a></p>
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/56819e7662924ccf91baa56999b5cbef" href="/{localLink:umb://document/56819e7662924ccf91baa56999b5cbef}" title="Lucerne">Lucerne</a> – St Moritz – <a data-udi="umb://document/2e09d5bd5fae466db4b3c37d49150722" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2e09d5bd5fae466db4b3c37d49150722}" title="Zermatt">Zermatt</a></strong></p>
<p><strong>10 nights</strong></p>
<p>This 10-day <a data-udi="umb://document/58868750b42d43d78a89df92df2b164f" href="/{localLink:umb://document/58868750b42d43d78a89df92df2b164f}" title="Swiss Classic Tour">self guided tour</a> is an excellent overview of Switzerland's special highlights. Designed for those seeking a true taste of this stunning country, including the beautiful lakeside setting of <a data-udi="umb://document/70b1a325037e4112bc5e6feeb41d725f" href="/{localLink:umb://document/70b1a325037e4112bc5e6feeb41d725f}" title="Lake Lucerne">Lake Lucerne,</a> with its pedestrianised Old Town and nearby Mount Pilatus. Plus unforgettable experiences on two of the most spectacular panoramic journeys in the world: the ‘Bernina’ and ‘Glacier Express’.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/58868750b42d43d78a89df92df2b164f" href="/{localLink:umb://document/58868750b42d43d78a89df92df2b164f}" title="Swiss Classic Tour"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<h3 style="color: #00533a;">Glorious Glacier Express</h3>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/ae29f8328e454cb08ae9ecf28f7078f4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae29f8328e454cb08ae9ecf28f7078f4}" title="Glacier Express"><strong><img src="/media/13067835/inghams-lakes-and-mountains-rail-holidays-glacier-express.jpg" alt="Glorious Glacier Express" data-udi="umb://media/a8081b98ca814e0caadf79dd78124035" /></strong></a></p>
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/7456bae57241449a84a68959b62b2aba" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7456bae57241449a84a68959b62b2aba}" title="Interlaken">Interlaken</a> – Zermatt – Davos/Klosters</strong></p>
<p><strong>10 or 11 nights</strong></p>
<p>Experience one of the most famous train lines in the world – the <a data-udi="umb://document/ae29f8328e454cb08ae9ecf28f7078f4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae29f8328e454cb08ae9ecf28f7078f4}" title="Glacier Express">Glacier Express</a>. Our 10 or 11 night independent rail holiday provides you with unforgettable views between Zermatt and either <a data-udi="umb://document/527f062dda374fee961e7ca5209c3d26" href="/{localLink:umb://document/527f062dda374fee961e7ca5209c3d26}" title="Davos">Davos</a> or <a data-udi="umb://document/5cdc3bd60ed74827b457178da3c4090e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5cdc3bd60ed74827b457178da3c4090e}" title="Klosters">Klosters</a>. The specially designed panoramic carriages unlock superb views over the Swiss Alps and you can pay locally to enjoy a 3 course set menu served to your seat. This is one epic train ride you don't want to miss.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/ae29f8328e454cb08ae9ecf28f7078f4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae29f8328e454cb08ae9ecf28f7078f4}" title="Glacier Express"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
<div></div>
<div class="g6">
<h3 style="color: #00533a;"><a name="Goldenpass"></a>GoldenPass Line</h3>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/d8a3be3fd1dd4a9393a346df4f3e910c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d8a3be3fd1dd4a9393a346df4f3e910c}" title="GoldenPass Line"><strong><img src="/media/13067836/inghams-lakes-and-mountains-rail-holidays-goldenpass-panorama.jpg" alt="GoldenPass Line" data-udi="umb://media/03b917d29a274d6eb45899441bece668" /></strong></a></p>
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/c98b896d425a4f9eb1d5e2464d2c17c2" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c98b896d425a4f9eb1d5e2464d2c17c2}" title="Montreux">Montreux</a> – <a data-udi="umb://document/dd4c4793225641fcb24c0918a33714b3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/dd4c4793225641fcb24c0918a33714b3}" title="Wengen">Wengen</a> – Lake Lucerne</strong></p>
<p><strong>10 or 11 nights</strong></p>
<p>Visit three very distinctive regions of <a data-udi="umb://document/92803bd348ec48c1b64d53e77931172d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/92803bd348ec48c1b64d53e77931172d}" title="Switzerland">Switzerland</a> on this three centre rail holiday which includes a trip on the <a data-udi="umb://document/d8a3be3fd1dd4a9393a346df4f3e910c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d8a3be3fd1dd4a9393a346df4f3e910c}" title="GoldenPass Line">GoldenPass line</a>. On your holiday you’ll have the opportunity to explore the Lavaux Vineyards, the mountainous Jungfrau area and the historical sites of Lucerne and many boat trips it offers from the shores of a stunning lake.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/d8a3be3fd1dd4a9393a346df4f3e910c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d8a3be3fd1dd4a9393a346df4f3e910c}" title="GoldenPass Line"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<h3 style="color: #00533a;">Venice Simplon-Orient-Express</h3>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/24f641b2cf3447309c8fe4a428627f89" href="/{localLink:umb://document/24f641b2cf3447309c8fe4a428627f89}" title="Venice Simplon Orient Express"><img src="/media/13070873/vsoe-bar-33.jpg" alt="Orient Express" data-udi="umb://media/662f62ab618b4e63a56d4f18e6e61f86" /></a></p>
<p>Step back into a bygone era with a once-in-a-lifetime journey on the <a data-udi="umb://document/24f641b2cf3447309c8fe4a428627f89" href="/{localLink:umb://document/24f641b2cf3447309c8fe4a428627f89}" title="Venice Simplon Orient Express">Venice Simplon-Orient-Express</a>. This famous train journey is a truly spectacular experience. Reviving the glitz and glamour of the 1920’s, the carriages of this iconic train have been painstakingly restored to their former glory. An attentive service and some of the best scenery in Europe promises to make this journey one you will never forget.<br /><br /><br /></p>
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/24f641b2cf3447309c8fe4a428627f89" href="/{localLink:umb://document/24f641b2cf3447309c8fe4a428627f89}" title="Venice Simplon Orient Express">Find out more &gt;</a></strong></p>
</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="g12">
<h3 style="color: #00533a; text-align: center;"><a name="Italy"></a>Trains from the UK to Italy</h3>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904}" title="Italy"><img src="/media/13071028/cinque_terre_italy.jpg" alt="Cinque Terre in Italy" data-udi="umb://media/cb110f6e066f4c5ab0c4a15cfc5d5fa2" /></a></p>
<p>Travelling from London to Italy by train is easy thanks to services from Eurostar to Paris and from Voyages SNCF onwards to Italy. From Paris, daytime services include a journey to <a data-udi="umb://document/2575554a5b50446eb00d5bf533f317cd" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2575554a5b50446eb00d5bf533f317cd}" title="Milan">Milan</a> or a high-speed train that travels through the Swiss Alps to <a data-udi="umb://document/7d421e04a79044babf8cafda30e31d4a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7d421e04a79044babf8cafda30e31d4a}" title="Lake Como">Lake Como</a> or <a data-udi="umb://document/476c8caf3fe84faab565f2d0f2e99f48" href="/{localLink:umb://document/476c8caf3fe84faab565f2d0f2e99f48}" title="Lake Maggiore">Lake Maggiore</a>. Overnight services depart from Paris in the early evening and arrive into Italy by morning. Cabins are available with two or three berths and they come equipped with a wash basin.</p>
</div>
<div> </div>
<div class="g6">
<h3 style="color: #00533a;">High speed trains</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13070922/rail-holidays-in-italy-2.jpg" alt="Rail Holidays in Italy" data-udi="umb://media/302e5c6c42304e45b91a80306d43eb2c" /></p>
<p>Trenitalia’s great network of high-speed rail routes makes touring <a data-udi="umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904}" title="Italy">Italy</a> a breeze. Major cities are all connected, from Turin all the way down to Salerno, and this is the best and most comfortable way to get between them. Services are frequent and carriages well equipped. You’ll be assigned a seat and have plenty of leg room to sit back and relax on your journey. If you book first class you’ll even be treated to a glass of prosecco as you embark.</p>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<h3 style="color: #00533a;">Regional Trains</h3>
<p><strong><span style="color: #7ea537;"><img src="/media/13070923/rail-holidays-in-italy-3.jpg" alt="Regional Rail holidays in Italy" data-udi="umb://media/1d95776134e944e0b98db173adf0e733" /></span></strong></p>
<p><span>These trains are perfect for onward travel to smaller towns like Siena and Viareggio. They have a slower pace so you’ll get to enjoy a bit of scenery before arriving at your destination. It’s also a great way to explore more of Italy on your holiday with day trips by train. From <a data-udi="umb://document/201893063f65496384a9bd17846543a7" href="/{localLink:umb://document/201893063f65496384a9bd17846543a7}" title="Venice">Venice,</a> take the train to Vicenza, head to Lucca from <a data-udi="umb://document/8b79e45930f145f6b156a9152415fa9b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/8b79e45930f145f6b156a9152415fa9b}" title="Florence">Florence</a> or jump on at <a data-udi="umb://document/1b38a4293ff04cc8b2dd360a57a538d8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1b38a4293ff04cc8b2dd360a57a538d8}" title="Sorrento">Sorrento</a> for a quick ride to Pompeii or Naples. </span></p>
</div>
<p> </p>
